<!--pages/education/education.wxml-->
<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <text class="title">水上安全教育培训</text>
  </view>
  
  <view class="card">
    <view class="section">
      <text class="section-title">救生知识</text>
      <text class="section-content">1. 发现溺水者时，首先确保自身安全\n2. 使用救生设备（救生圈、浮板）进行救援\n3. 拨打紧急救援电话 110/120</text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="section">
      <text class="section-title">急救措施</text>
      <text class="section-content">1. 将溺水者救上岸后，立即检查呼吸心跳\n2. 如无呼吸，立即进行心肺复苏(CPR)\n3. 保持溺水者体温，等待专业救援</text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="section">
      <text class="section-title">预防措施</text>
      <text class="section-content">1. 儿童需在成人监护下玩水\n2. 避免在陌生水域游泳\n3. 饮酒后禁止下水</text>
    </view>
  </view>
  
  <!-- 视频教程 -->
  <view class="video-section">
  <text class="section-title">教学视频</text>
  <view class="video-container">
    <view class="video-loading" wx:if="{{videoLoading}}">
      <text>视频加载中...</text>
    </view>
    <video 
      src="{{videoSrc}}" 
      controls 
      autoplay="{{false}}"
      bindloadstart="onVideoLoadStart"
      bindloadedmetadata="onVideoLoaded"
      style="width: 100%; height: 400rpx;"
    ></video>
  </view>
  <text class="video-desc">水上安全救援教学视频</text>
</view>
  
  <button class="back-btn" bindtap="goBack">返回首页</button>
</view>